short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Play games in GitHub's contribution graph.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension replaces GitHub's contribution graph with a random game. Open your console to have the list of controls.
It's super easy to create your own game, have a look at: https://github.com/Zhouzi/contrib-awakens
